    • getTeams

      public HashMap<Integer,TeamModel> getTeams()
      Gets the current collection of teams. If this HashMap is altered, and QuizRegister::saveQuiz is called, The changes made WILL be reflected in the database. In the HashMap, the key is the id of the team, while the value is the team object.
      Returns:
      The teams that are registered to this quiz.

    • getTeamsSortedByScore

      public Iterator<TeamModel> getTeamsSortedByScore()
      Get all teams that are part of a team, sorted in descending order according to their score.
      Returns:
      The teams of the quiz in descending order according to their score.

    • setTeams

      protected void setTeams(HashMap<Integer,TeamModel> teams)
      Sets the teams of this quiz. This is done at object creation by the QuizDAO.
      Parameters:
      teams - The new HashMap of the teams. The key is the id of the team, while the value is the corresponding team object.

    • getQuestions

      public HashMap<Integer,QuestionModel> getQuestions()
      Gets the current collection of questions. If this HashMap is altered, and QuizRegister::saveQuiz is called, The changes made WILL be reflected in the database. In the HashMap, the key is the id of the question, while the value is the question object.
      Returns:
      The questions that are registered to this quiz.

    • setQuestions

      protected void setQuestions(HashMap<Integer,QuestionModel> questions)
      Sets the questions of this quiz. This is done at object creation by the QuizDAO.
      Parameters:
      questions - The new HashMap of the teams. The key is the id of the question, while the value is the corresponding question object.

    • getCombinedTeamScore

      public double getCombinedTeamScore()

    • getDifficulty

      public double getDifficulty()
      Returns:
      The difficulty on a scale from 0 (hardest) to 1 (easiest) if no teams are registered to this quiz, -1 is returned.
